T(aP + bQ)(X) = (aP + bQ)'(X)+(X-2)(aP + bQ)(X)\\ = aP'(X) + bQ'(X) + (X-2)aP(X) + (X-2)bQ(X)\\ T(aP + bQ)(X)= aT(P)(X) + bT(P)(X) 
